cast.original_title: Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again
cast.overview: Five years after meeting her three fathers, Sophie Sheridan prepares to open her mother’s hotel. In 1979, young Donna Sheridan meets the men who each could be Sophie’s biological father.
cast.title: Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again

details.biography: Alexa Davies is a Welsh actress born in 1995. She is best known for her comedy roles; including Aretha in  Raised by Wolves, Yvonne in BBC2's Cradle to Grave and Kate in BBC4's detectorists. In 2018 she starred as young Rosie in Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again.
details.name: Alexa Davies
